article.headline: White's 18 points lead Temple past Navy 75-68
article.description: — Jahlil White's 18 points helped Temple defeat Navy 75-68 on Friday night.
article.linkText: White's 18 points lead Temple past Navy 75-68
article.story: ANNAPOLIS, Md. -- — Jahlil White's 18 points helped Temple defeat Navy 75-68 on Friday night. White also added 10 rebounds for the Owls (2-0). Hysier Miller scored 18 points while going 6 of 15 from the floor, including 3 for 9 from 3-point range, and 3 for 7 from the line, and added five rebounds and five steals. Matteo Picarelli was 4 of 12 shooting, including 4 for 10 from 3-point range, and went 5 for 6 from the line to finish with 17 points. Austin Benigni finished with 13 points for the Midshipmen (0-2). Donovan Draper added nine points, 12 rebounds and four steals for Navy. Kam Summers also had nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
